1
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,960
[Episode 4: Make Her Regret]

2
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:14,365
Ren Xi Zhou.

3
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:17,504
Ren Xi Zhou!

4
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,599
What?

5
00:01:27,599 --> 00:01:29,797
Never seen a bike chain fall off?

6
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:34,705
We can cooperate.

7
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,040
I can improve the recipe,

8
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,239
and in exchange,

9
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:40,067
you can be my script consultant.

10
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,527
Script consultant?

11
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:46,113
To inspire and enrich me.

12
00:01:48,178 --> 00:01:49,640
Like...

13
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,140
recently.

14
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,207
Deal.

15
00:02:10,640 --> 00:02:12,060
Wait for me.

16
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:22,246
This is my number.

17
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,242
See you tomorrow.

18
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,400
See you tomorrow.

19
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,760
What?

20
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,329
See you tomorrow.

21
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,796
<i>See you tomorrow.</i>

22
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,728
Thank you.

23
00:03:26,728 --> 00:03:28,126
[Huang Ying De]

24
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,113
Hello?

25
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,484
Hello?

26
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:39,360
You forgot yourself.

27
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,919
Why are you distracted?

28
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:42,154
Nothing.

29
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,350
That's good then.

30
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,719
Not me.

31
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:51,302
But a friend of mine.

32
00:03:58,857 --> 00:04:01,199
Working with an ex can be awkward.

33
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,690
But...

34
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,480
<i>No.</i>

35
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,091
<i>Why should I hide?</i>

36
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,360
For a better job,

37
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,560
she discarded your pal.

38
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,879
Now your pal is successful

39
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:14,852
and elated, isn't it good?

40
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,839
He's disappointed.

41
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,049
Disappointed?

42
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:19,879
She looks even

43
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:21,519
more radiant than ever.

44
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:22,712
Why?

45
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:32,120
Why isn't she suffering

46
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,040
or even regretful?

47
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,790
Thinking like that means you've already lost.

48
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,328
So make her regret.

49
00:04:48,088 --> 00:04:49,880
[Nanwan Liangpi]

50
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,199
Auntie Qiu left.

51
00:04:58,199 --> 00:05:00,120
Can you handle it alone?

52
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,959
Are you a boomerang kid?

53
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:05,160
Nice words do you no harm.

54
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:07,519
I'm just in a gap.

55
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,519
Besides,

56
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:10,116
I can help you.

57
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,000
This... this isn't good.

58
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,840
Bitten by insects all over.

59
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,125
Today...

60
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,519
I went to another stall.

61
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:20,751
It seems that the owner is dishonest.

62
00:05:21,639 --> 00:05:23,439
Because you fool around until midnight

63
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,480
and sleep in,

64
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,720
you have to pick what's left.

65
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,120
I fool around?

66
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,639
To improve your recipe,

67
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:31,543
I'm busy until midnight.

68
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,603
Where's the recipe?

69
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:41,482
Where are my books on the desk?

70
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:43,639
It's a mess.

71
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:46,175
I threw away all the useless things.

72
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,360
How could you throw them away
without my permission?

73
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:51,993
There are my culinary notes.

74
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:57,071
You shall tidy up what's useful by yourself.

75
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,360
Considering your temper,

76
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,199
I know why Auntie Qiu left.

77
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:02,723
You know nothing.

78
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,480
Where are you going?

79
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,935
None of your business.

80
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,542
The dishes are almost ready.

81
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,880
Why do you keep so many vegetables
instead of selling them?

82
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:37,759
Because I'll eat them myself.

83
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:39,532
Then why do you sell vegetables?

84
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:09,536
<i>Believe it or not,
I'll take all your vegetables.</i>

85
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,843
<i>So make her regret.</i>

86
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,199
Make her

87
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,240
regret.

88
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:17,079
<i>As fragrant flowers attract butterflies,</i>

89
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:18,360
<i>we can win</i>

90
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:20,040
<i>her heart with our charm</i>

91
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,079
<i>and make her regret.</i>

92
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:24,000
<i>I don't want anything to do with her.</i>

93
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,480
<i>I just</i>

94
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:28,560
<i>sincerely hope she suffers from</i>

95
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,120
leaving me,

96
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,759
even if

97
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:33,760
only a little.

98
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,995
Who are you greeting?

99
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,665
Over there.

100
00:07:52,066 --> 00:07:53,079
Where?

101
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:54,700
Over there.

102
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:05,000
[Qiuping Diner]

103
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,360
Auntie Qiu!

104
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,160
- You're here!
- Another new dish?

105
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,495
- Try it, try it.
- Okay.

106
00:08:09,495 --> 00:08:10,500
What do you think?

107
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:11,875
- Good?
- It's good.

108
00:08:11,875 --> 00:08:13,600
Come in. Here.

109
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,000
- As usual?
- Yes.

110
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:18,000
Missy, you look familiar. Are you local?

111
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,000
I returned recently.

112
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,642
Here, try it.

113
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:30,000
<i>I know why Auntie Qiu left.</i>

114
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,484
<i>You know nothing.</i>

115
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,604
[Qiuping Diner Specialties]

116
00:08:36,604 --> 00:08:38,995
Same menu as ours.

117
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,840
So she learned the craft and

118
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:44,109
was eager to start her own business.

119
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,790
What do you think?

120
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:50,399
Tough meat, bland seasoning,

121
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,603
oily cabinets,

122
00:08:51,603 --> 00:08:52,680
shameless owner!

123
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,760
You!

124
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,360
I remember.

125
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,840
- You're...
- Zero point.

126
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,960
You brat!

127
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,440
I held you when you were little.

128
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,673
You'll be driven away whenever you come.

129
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:11,580
My hands!

130
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,840
<i>That brat</i>

131
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,580
<i>really pondered over it.</i>

132
00:09:46,402 --> 00:09:48,615
[Hongxia Diner Menu]

133
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:46,595
You found my notebook?

134
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,399
Under the bed.

135
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:51,043
I had a try.

136
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,755
It tastes good.

137
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,940
What happened to your hands?

138
00:11:05,639 --> 00:11:07,463
You went through the trash?

139
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,075
Idlers would do that.

140
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,905
Nice words do you no harm.

141
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,759
One-week probation.

142
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:33,320
If you do well, you can stay.

143
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,720
If you don't,

144
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:36,192
get another job.

145
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,160
The other hand.

146
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:45,120
Wang Qiu Ping's restaurant has a signature dish

147
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,440
called flavorful mackerel.

148
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,480
If you can make a better dish
than it in a week,

149
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,920
you can stay.

150
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:52,120
That's too harsh.

151
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,520
So you give up?

152
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:55,200
I won't.

153
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,759
Don't go back on your word.

154
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:58,080
You're not a kid anymore.

155
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,400
Don't go back on your word.

156
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,842
I know!

157
00:12:17,152 --> 00:12:18,639
<i>After dinner,</i>

158
00:12:18,639 --> 00:12:21,000
<i>I walked with Mom.</i>

159
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,083
You said "See you tomorrow".

160
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,178
Hello?

161
00:12:35,178 --> 00:12:36,640
<i>Hello. It's me, it's me, it's me.</i>

162
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:38,720
<i>I called you this morning.</i>

163
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,840
Mr. Huang,

164
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,973
what's up?

165
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:44,600
<i>It's about the script you wrote last week.</i>

166
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:47,240
<i>Can you make a flyer for me?</i>

167
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,799
<i>Buddy, not for free.</i>

168
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:51,800
<i>When it wraps, I'll ask the producer</i>

169
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:53,679
<i>to credit you as a script consultant.
What do you think?</i>

170
00:12:53,679 --> 00:12:55,280
When do you need it?

171
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:58,080
<i>By tomorrow morning. Before 7 AM.</i>

172
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,240
Too early.

173
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,720
<i>Nan Feng,</i>

174
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,080
<i>we've been dudes</i>

175
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,120
<i>for years!</i>

176
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,280
<i>Do me a favor!</i>

177
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:06,159
Send me the requirements.

178
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,679
<i>No problem, no problem!</i>

179
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:09,027
<i>With my gratitude.</i>

180
00:13:33,559 --> 00:13:34,895
What do you think?

181
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,350
Have you suggested your pal?

182
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:45,160
I heard his ex is...

183
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:47,794
stubborn, once she makes up her mind,

184
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,919
she seldom regrets.

185
00:13:49,919 --> 00:13:51,420
Not even once?

186
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:56,936
<i>Hurry up!</i>

187
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,573
<i>Go!</i>

188
00:14:06,519 --> 00:14:07,920
<i>You want to annoy me?</i>

189
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:09,529
<i>Run, you idiot!</i>

190
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,415
Only once.
